FT  03 OCT 94 / Equity Markets: Other markets - Frankfurt
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
After today's unification holiday, the market will increasingly be
influenced by opinion polls ahead of the federal election on October 16. UBS
expects a continuation of the volatility in the stock market to be combined
with a sideways trend in the run up to the polls.
On the corporate front, Allianz holds its annual meeting on Wednesday while
Thursday and Friday bring the annual meeting of the chemical association.
UBS says that volume in the domestic chemical sector was up 4 per cent in
the first half of this year.
