<HEADLINE>
FT  03 OCT 94 / International Company News: Shell Australia
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Shell Australia has released details of the planned flotation of its
minerals business, which is being packaged into a new company called Acacia
Resources. It said 200m Acacia shares - 100 per cent of the company's equity
 -would be offered at ADollars 2 each.
