<DATELINE>
   BANGKOK
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
The Stock Exchange of Thailand has awarded new brokerage seats to four
companies which were previously sub-brokers: the upgrading of Jardine
Fleming Thanakom, Nithiphat, Ekachart and Prime brings the total number of
full brokers to 44, writes Victor Mallet in Bangkok.
